      <title>白宫说，特朗普的关税要立即生效。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-april-2-tariffs-to-take-immediate-effect-white-house-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周三宣布后，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的全面关税将立即生效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-april-2-tariffs-to-take-immediate-effect-white-house-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 16:33:40 GMT</pubDate>
