    <item>
      <title>普林斯顿说，美国机构已暂停数十个赠款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/princeton-says-government-agencies-suspend-dozens-of-grants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[普林斯顿大学说，随着唐纳德·特朗普总统升级他与精英美国大学的战斗，美国政府机构已经冻结了数十项研究补助金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/princeton-says-government-agencies-suspend-dozens-of-grants</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 16:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国贸易办公室针对魁北克的法语法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-trade-office-takes-aim-at-quebec-s-french-language-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国以魁北克有争议的法语法作为贸易的障碍，这一举动可能会使加拿大对唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税做出反应的决定更加复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-trade-office-takes-aim-at-quebec-s-french-language-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 15:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普官员承认驱逐涉嫌MS-13成员的错误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-officials-admit-error-in-deporting-suspected-ms-13-member</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府表示，尽管移民法官的命令将涉嫌的MS-13帮派成员驱逐到埃尔萨尔瓦多监狱，但除了移民法官的命令将其撤职到该国，但犯了“行政错误”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-officials-admit-error-in-deporting-suspected-ms-13-member</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 15:57:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
